	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />MMC1 has been produced on a CPLD by RetroZone ( retrousb.com ) but the original ASICs obviously have not been made in a long time. If someone did decap the mappers then ofcourse people could reproduce them most likely by using some programmable device as no one is ever going to have the volume of cartridges to actually have the ASICs produced again.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
