		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">MMC1 is a known known: all 20 latches in that thing are well documented.</div>
<br />25 latches actually (I guess you forgot the temporary shift register).
<br />
<br />Unfortunately the MMC1 is a known unknown as well : I think the effect of RMW instrucitons on the MMC1 is still mysterious, such as the difference between original MMC1, MMC1A, MMC1B1 and MMC1B2.

		

		</td>
